  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, as our unfortunate hero was walking home, a demon stopped him on the road.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without warning, she cast a spell on him, knocking him unconscious. When he awoke, he found himself in a mysterious castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There, a maid explained to him that he was captured in order to serve as a demon's slave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can our hero escape? Or is he doomed to serve for the rest of his life?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeon crawling action RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore randomized dungeons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather materials and craft items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power up and try to escape the demon's castle</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, as our unfortunate hero was walking home, a demon stopped him on the road.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without warning, she cast a spell on him, knocking him unconscious. When he awoke, he found himself in a mysterious castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There, a maid explained to him that he was captured in order to serve as a demon's slave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can our hero escape? Or is he doomed to serve for the rest of his life?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeon crawling action RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore randomized dungeons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather materials and craft items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power up and try to escape the demon's castle</p></li></ul>",
